data.description:
Welcome to your new home!  The sellers are offering up to $3,000 in closing assistance or to help buy down the interest rate for the buyer with an accepted offer.  

This beautiful single level ranch home situated on a large gentle lot is move in ready and waiting for you.  The home features a 2 car attached garage that is heated. There are updates throughout the home to welcome you.  There is a pantry space in the kitchen, a new gas range, fresh paint and new butcher block countertops, tile backsplash, and recessed lighting has been added to the home.  There is a new live edge bar for grabbing a quick snack.  New tile has been installed in the guest bathroom. New rustic trim invites you into each room. New flooring throughout the home greets you as you enter through the updated covered front porch.  New vinyl siding, updated fascia and gutters finish out the exterior of the home.  There are updates in every area of this home. The large back yard features a storage shed to help keep the home decluttered, and a fire pit for enjoying those peaceful East Tennessee evenings.
